                       String method,
                       String route,

                throws KyrioException
        Invokes REST operation on the server and handles the response.
        Parameters:
        type - Expected type of response object.
        method - Operation method: GET, POST, PUT or DELETE
        route - Operation base route.
        parameters - Operation query parameter.
        body - Value to be sent in request body.
        Returns:
        Value returned by the server of expected type.
        Throws:
        KyrioException - returned by Kyrio server.
